Class AssignmentMetaData

java.lang.Object
com.example.cmscdocs.AssignmentMetaData
public class AssignmentMetaData extends Object
This contains all the data inputted by the user. Such data element class was created due to abstraction and easier retrieval of data between classes that interact with it.
Author:
